    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and the suspension feels a bit soft. Visually, the paint has some fading on the roof and hood, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and a few small tears. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a bit of character and potential minor maintenance in the near future.",
