    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute showpiece, maintained to a standard that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster with zero blemishes or rock chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and free of wear, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic component operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service history and strictly garage-kept ownership. With exceptionally low mileage and a smoke-free interior, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine, investment-grade condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
